80
00:08:50.618 --> 00:08:51.685
I hated it.

81
00:08:51.786 --> 00:08:53.754
You hated it.

82
00:08:53.855 --> 00:08:54.856
Okay.

83
00:08:54.956 --> 00:08:57.058
You didn't give it enough time.

84
00:08:57.158 --> 00:08:59.126
- Rip didn't go to school.
- Don't think Rip

85
